leve.name: Vanishing Point
leve.description: The Calamity has left its mark ever so close to the Gate of the Sultana. Ruins of once-gracious homes yet remain, their shattered hulks a brooding reminder of forces beyond our reckoning. Such a reminder is neither healthful nor politic, and we seek industrious Disciples to remove all traces.
leve.client: Amajina & Sons Minekeep, Adelard the Able
